00:46:42.900 --> 00:46:45.030
principle.

00:46:45.030 --> 00:46:46.830
So the Lagrangian
is very-- actually,

00:46:46.830 --> 00:46:51.833
if you write the Lagrangian, it
looks very similar to this one.

00:46:51.833 --> 00:46:52.750
Looks similar to this.

00:46:55.490 --> 00:46:57.490
The question you're asking
the mechanical system

00:46:57.490 --> 00:47:00.487
