00:48:38.672 --> 00:48:40.380
Now confuse my mind
with science somehow.

00:48:48.580 --> 00:48:51.052
Well, anyway.

00:48:51.052 --> 00:49:02.213
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]

00:49:02.213 --> 00:49:03.880
