01:39:43.510 --> 01:39:49.000
but whether the pattern is dark
or bright at any given instant

01:39:49.000 --> 01:39:52.450
actually depends on how
the two waves started.

01:39:52.450 --> 01:39:56.470
So when we have-- this
is quantum superposition,

01:39:56.470 --> 01:40:01.010
